article.headline: Air Force 63, TCU 45
article.story: FORT WORTH, Texas (AP) -- Antoine Hood scored 23 points to lead Air Force to a 63-45 victory over TCU on Wednesday night. Hood hit 9-of-16 from the field, including 3-of-5 from 3-point range. He also had four steals. Jacob Burtschi added 16 points, hitting 7-of-11 from the field. He also had seven rebounds and three steals. Air Force (20-5, 8-4 Mountain West) led 35-17 at the half and shot 50 percent from the field. TCU (5-20, 1-10) shot 37 percent from the field. Judson Stubbs led TCU (5-20, 1-10) with 11 points. He also had seven rebounds. Air Force scored 25 points off of 19 TCU turnovers.
